            <h3 class="beta">Bonhams</h3>

            <p>Neon has partnered with <a href="https://www.bonhams.com/" rel="external">Bonhams</a>, the fine art auction house, on a number of events. This has allowed us to gain a deeper understanding of how our technology intersects with the art world. Read about our recent event where we discussed parallels between art and tech on our <a href="https://medium.com/neon-blog/chasing-the-unicorn-2eeddf09de34" rel="me">blog</a> or in the <a href="http://blogs.wsj.com/digits/2015/10/09/what-venture-capital-and-art-have-in-common/" rel="external">Wall Street Journal</a>.</p>

