            <h3 class="beta">Customer advisory board</h3>

            <p>Neon partners with customer advisors from leading companies including <a href="http://www.bloomberg.com/" rel="external">Bloomberg</a>. Our customer advisors provide insight on trends and serve as beta testers for new Neon products and features. The group meets yearly in our offices in San Francisco for in depth sessions on industry advancements and emerging needs in editorial, brand, and e-commerce. Interested in learning more about our customer advisory board? Get in touch at <a href="mailto:<%=data.config.partners_email%>"><%=data.config.partners_email%></a>.</p>
